Package benak.tomas.crimemonitor.library

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UtvarAndIntervalBasedCrimeSummary
    A base interface for providing a crime data interval context.
    UtvarBasedCrimeSummary
    A base interface for providing a department code and name.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CrimeMonthHistogramObservation
    A class used to represent an observation of the number of committed crimes during a particular month in a particular year.
    CrimesList
    A class used to represent a crime ranking for all kinds of crimes.
    CrimesSummary
    A class used to provide the statistics for all crimes for a particular police department and crime data interval.
    CrimesSummaryBasic
    A base class used to hold some basic crime statistics related to a particular department and crime data interval.
    CrimeSummary
    A class used to record an information how many times a given crime has been committed.
    CrimeSummaryDetailed
    A class used to provide the crime statistics for a particular kind of crime.
    CrimeSummaryWithUtvarAndIntervalBase
    A base class associating the contained crime statistics with a particular crime data interval.
    CrimeSummaryWithUtvarBase
    A base class associating the contained crime statistics with a particular police department and code.
    CrimeUtvarDetail
    A class used to provide an information about the territorial units covered by a given police department.
    UtvarKodANazev
    A class used to hold the information about a code and name for a particular police department.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CrimeMeasureTrend
    An enumeration used to describe the trend for the committed crimes count over the period of time.
